text:
Speciality for food - is their "Prata on the Go" & "Satay in the cup" with delicious taste of gravy that brings you back to the legendary taste of spices. Indeed Excellent Taste 😋😋😋
Good to go along with their
SpecialTea - ooh Great Taste from the Holy Land Arabian Tea Superbly Good 👍
HIGHLY RECOMMENDED
